title: GDG DevFest Hyderabad 2016 Summary
brief: GDG DevFest Hyderabad 2016 was a great success. We are happy to share with you some facts, emotions and, of course, photos from the biggest Google Developers Conference in Hyderabad!

title: GDG DevFest 2017 Announced
brief: Google Developers Group Hyderabad is proud to announce the sixth annual GDG DevFest 2017 which is the biggest Google related event in Hyderabad carefully crafted by GDG community! The event will take place on **7th of October** in **Hyderabad**.

title: Call for Papers - DevFest 2017
brief: GDG DevFest Hyderabad 2017 is announced! The 6th edition of the biggest conference about Google technologies in Hyderabad will take on **October 7 , 2017**. That means that it is time to open [call for talk submissions](http://bit.ly/df16-c4p).
